for Prevention," NIDA Research Monograph 56, DHHS Publication No. ADM 85-1335, Washington, 
DC, 1985.
<P><LI>  Cited in Stern, op. cit.; R. H. Coombs, "Peers vs Parental Influence in Substance Use Among 
Hispanic and Anglo Children and Adolescents," Journal of Youth and Adolescents, Vol. 20, No. 1, 
1991.
<P><LI>  Quentin J. Schultze, op. cit, pp. 12-13.
<P><LI>  Lois Haight, "Criminal Beginnings - The Use of Illegal Drugs," published by Committees of 
Correspondence, Inc., February 8, 1994.
</OL>
</FONT>

<p>

